<p class="ayah 96-2" id="2" ><span class=""><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">خَلَقَ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">He created</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">ٱلْإِنسَـٰنَ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">man</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">مِنْ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">from</span></span><span class="word staticWord"><span class="ar quranText top first rtl" dir="rtl">عَلَقٍ</span><span class="en second ltr" dir="ltr">a clinging substance.</span></span></span> <span class="verse-number"><span class="icon leftBracket"> </span>2<span class="icon rightBracket"> </span></span></p>
